{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-excerpt-js","path":"/excerpts/nature_bonfire/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>From beckoning to threatening,<br>\nChanges with changes of the wind,<br>\nBellow where Roman icons reign,<br>\nA struggle to force chaos tame,<br>\nWakefires see the night fear defeat,<br>\nChills are so quick to turn to sweat,<br>\nViolent flames spit where we sit,<br>\nSun caught, captured and then relit,<br>\nSmoke and flame embraced in a dance,<br>\nSat centre stage to a drunken song,<br>\nVerve that strives to make it to dawn,<br>\nNothing but embers come the morn,<br>\nPast midnight slowly in retreat,<br>\nSway of flames to keep at bay sleep,<br>\nA comfort, a blistering heat,<br>\nA hunger that's too great to meet.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 09, 2020","title":"Bonfire","audio":null,"icon":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/9705b4ea7437974c86891f6e924c995d/7d509/nature_poem_a_bonfire.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9705b4ea7437974c86891f6e924c995d/f836f/nature_poem_a_bonfire.jpg 200w,\n/static/9705b4ea7437974c86891f6e924c995d/2244e/nature_poem_a_bonfire.jpg 400w,\n/static/9705b4ea7437974c86891f6e924c995d/7d509/nature_poem_a_bonfire.jpg 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/excerpts/nature_bonfire/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}